And chanel is loaded.

25:23.456 --> 25:25.222
So, huh, doi, neckbrace,

25:25.224 --> 25:27.391
That's who I'm bringing home
to meet my parents.

25:27.393 --> 25:28.959
Well...

25:30.696 --> 25:32.563
