how it goes

25:32.565 --> 25:35.132
Bringing chanel home
for thanksgiving.

25:35.134 --> 25:37.167
Yeah, I guess we will see,

25:37.169 --> 25:38.802
As that's what's going
to happen.

25:38.804 --> 25:40.304
I guess we'll just have
to wait and see.

25:40.306 --> 25:42.072
Yeah, we will wait and see,

25:42.074 --> 25:43.841
As thanksgiving is an event
that takes place in the future

25:43.843 --> 25:45.476
And therefore
it hasn't happened yet.

25:45.478 --> 25:46.677
We'll see.

25:46.679 --> 25:48.145
Yep, sure will.

25:48.147 --> 25:49.813
As the arrow of time
flows in one direction,

25:49.815 --> 25:51.916
Causing future events to flow
inexorably towards us.

25:51.918 --> 25:52.917
(blows)

25:52.919 --> 25:54.018
Wh...

25:54.020 --> 25:55.319
Okay, just so we're clear,

25:55.321 --> 25:57.988
I only caught this kiss...

25:57.990 --> 25:59.423
So I could throw it away.

26:06.832 --> 26:08.065
(vacuum sealer buzzing)

26:08.067 --> 26:10.568
I can't do this.

26:11.837 --> 26:13.337
I can't believe it.

26:13.339 --> 26:15.239
Earl grey is dead.

26:15.241 --> 26:17.741
It had to be boone
who killed him.

26:17.743 --> 26:19.209
You know what I can't believe?!

26:19.211 --> 26:21.078
I cannot believe that no one
is comforting me

26:21.080 --> 26:23.714
After I was almost murdered
by the red devil,

26:23.716 --> 26:24.915
Who was in the back seat
of my car

26:24.917 --> 26:26.584
And then barely escaped

26:26.586 --> 26:29.086
As some poor old
truck driver

26:29.088 --> 26:30.421
Was hacked to death
with a machete!

26:30.423 --> 26:31.922
And then, you know,

26:31.924 --> 26:33.591
I thought I'd at least
get some props

26:33.593 --> 26:36.527
For coming back with such
an amazing scary story.

26:36.529 --> 26:38.028
