Actually, number five,

26:38.030 --> 26:40.197
That story is neither scary
nor amazing.

26:40.199 --> 26:43.200
That story is an exact facsimile
of the hook hand story

26:43.202 --> 26:44.602
Hester told about an hour ago.

26:44.604 --> 26:46.370
Honestly, if you're going
to get attacked,

26:46.372 --> 26:48.906
Please attempt to get attacked
in a fresh, exciting way.

26:48.908 --> 26:51.241
We have to concentrate--
the pieces of this puzzle

26:51.243 --> 26:52.743
Are coming together.

26:52.745 --> 26:54.812
Yes, we know now that
boone is the red devil.

26:54.814 --> 26:56.714
There's more than one
red devil, moron.

26:56.716 --> 26:58.382
Well, now we know boone
is one of them.

26:58.384 --> 27:00.484
Which means he's probably
the baby in the bathtub.

27:00.486 --> 27:02.252
Zayday:
We should call the police.

27:02.254 --> 27:04.154
They've got to find him.

27:04.156 --> 27:05.923
Grace:
Already did. The police put out
an all-points bulletin

27:05.925 --> 27:08.325
And denise is aiding
the manhunt.

27:08.327 --> 27:09.760
The police aren't going
to help us.

27:09.762 --> 27:11.996
You can't stop a ghost.

27:11.998 --> 27:13.163
Oh, my god,

27:13.165 --> 27:14.598
I'm so freaked out.

27:14.600 --> 27:15.766
Will someone please
tell a ghost story?

27:15.768 --> 27:17.167
Hester:
I have a ghost story.

27:17.169 --> 27:18.602
It's a good one.

27:18.604 --> 27:21.338
It's about a girl
who never fit in.

27:21.340 --> 27:22.940
As much as she tried
to be popular,

27:22.942 --> 27:24.942
The mean girls were always
trying to tear her down.

27:24.944 --> 27:27.277
They could never see past
her neckbrace.

27:27.279 --> 27:29.647
She soon realized
the only way to get back

27:29.649 --> 27:31.782
At these girls would be
to screw chanel's boyfriend,

27:31.784 --> 27:36.086
Chad radwell,
and wreak ultimate vengeance.

27:36.088 --> 27:38.922
What?
That's right, chanel,

27:38.924 --> 27:40.257
Her name is me.

27:40.259 --> 27:42.326
And guess what, bitch,
I'm pregnant!

27:43.929 --> 27:45.763
This is insane.

27:45.765 --> 27:47.264
Looks like I'll be going
to the hamptons

27:47.266 --> 27:49.099
For thanksgiving
with the radwells.

27:49.101 --> 27:52.569
(quietly):
Guess who's top bitch
on campus now, chanel?

27:54.940 --> 27:57.408
(creaking)

27:59.612 --> 28:01.345
Are you still packing?

28:01.347 --> 28:03.681
Uh, excuse me for taking pride
in a quality pack job, chanel.

28:03.683 --> 28:05.649
Packing matters to me.

28:05.651 --> 28:07.851
That's why I chose to minor
in luggage sciences

28:07.853 --> 28:09.687
With an emphasis
in packing theory.

28:09.689 --> 28:11.722
Is it true about hester?

28:16.295 --> 28:17.594
She's pregnant.

28:19.498 --> 28:22.032
(sighs heavily)

28:22.034 --> 28:24.034
(quietly):
Oh, man.

28:24.036 --> 28:26.303
Oh, no.

28:26.305 --> 28:29.239
Oh...

28:29.241 --> 28:31.408
I really screwed up.

28:31.410 --> 28:33.143
So it's true?

28:33.145 --> 28:35.212
(chad sighs)

28:35.214 --> 28:37.147
I guess so.

28:37.149 --> 28:39.516
I mean, most of the time
we porked in a way

28:39.518 --> 28:41.385
That could not result
in pregnancy,

28:41.387 --> 28:42.720
If you know what I mean.

28:43.889 --> 28:45.489
(sighs)

28:45.491 --> 28:48.325
But I always knew I had
a sackful of strong swimmers.

28:49.161 --> 28:50.494
Chad.

28:50.496 --> 28:52.362
I'm sorry, chanel.

28:52.364 --> 28:54.565
Look, I'm as pissed off
about this as you are.

28:54.567 --> 28:57.334
That hester chick
is weird.

28:57.336 --> 29:00.337
Tossing her the bone
was not even all that fun.

29:00.339 --> 29:02.940
But I guess
I got to marry her now.

29:04.243 --> 29:05.743
Take her home to thanksgiving.

29:05.745 --> 29:06.744
Wait, what?!

29:06.746 --> 29:08.078
I'm sorry, chanel,

29:08.080 --> 29:09.546
That's just how
the radwells roll.

29:09.548 --> 29:11.181
We make our beds
and we lie in them.

29:12.418 --> 29:14.251
We lie in them
with our

29:14.253 --> 29:16.820
Creepy neckbraced
scoliosis wives.

29:18.057 --> 29:20.424
But look...

29:20.426 --> 29:23.060
You could still be
my piece on the side.

29:23.062 --> 29:25.629
No, this is not happening!

29:25.631 --> 29:27.264
I will not tolerate
being treated this way,

29:27.266 --> 29:29.066
Do you understand?

29:29.068 --> 29:30.601
This is the last straw.

29:30.603 --> 29:32.069
I'm sorry, chanel. I am.

29:32.071 --> 29:34.605
I-I... I just don't get
what you want me to do.

29:34.607 --> 29:35.739
I want you to pay.

29:35.741 --> 29:37.908
Okay, uh, hold on. What?

29:37.910 --> 29:39.543
You heard me.

29:39.545 --> 29:42.045
You are gonna pay, big-time,
for this, chad radwell.

29:42.047 --> 29:44.581
You might even just pay
the ultimate price.

29:44.583 --> 29:46.917
Ultimate...?
Wait, hold up.

29:46.919 --> 29:48.318
Did you just threaten
to kill me?

29:51.590 --> 29:54.324
Chanel, are you the killer?

29:55.561 --> 29:57.828
I guess we'll see.

30:06.605 --> 30:07.971
Chanel #3, #5?

30:07.973 --> 30:10.307
I owe you both the most
heartfelt of apologies.

30:10.309 --> 30:11.575
Remember when I said
that the only thing

30:11.577 --> 30:13.110
A sorority's ever been good for

30:13.112 --> 30:14.678
Is scoring a hot, rich husband?

30:14.680 --> 30:17.080
Well, I have never been
so wrong.

30:17.082 --> 30:19.283
Kappa house is,
and always has been,

30:19.285 --> 30:21.585
First and foremost,
a sisterhood

30:21.587 --> 30:23.086
And I have never needed
my sisters

30:23.088 --> 30:24.354
More than I need them now.

30:24.356 --> 30:26.089
Yeah, okay, apology accepted.

30:26.091 --> 30:27.691
Hold on.

30:27.693 --> 30:30.794
I am not just going to accept
any old apology, chanel.

30:30.796 --> 30:32.930
I mean, you treat me
like garbage every single day.

30:32.932 --> 30:35.432
Am I just supposed to ignore
the obvious fact

30:35.434 --> 30:37.100
That you hate me
and love nothing more

30:37.102 --> 30:39.436
Than playing super-humiliating
pranks on me?

30:39.438 --> 30:41.772
Why do you always have to make
everything about you?

30:41.774 --> 30:43.040
Like, remember that one time

30:43.042 --> 30:44.274
When you hacked into
my mom's e-mail

30:44.276 --> 30:45.542
And wrote me
this really long letter

30:45.544 --> 30:46.944
Explaining how I was adopted

30:46.946 --> 30:49.780
And born with
fetal alcohol syndrome

30:49.782 --> 30:52.216
And therefore, had an iq
in the low 60s?

30:52.218 --> 30:54.484
I'm sorry,
but that was hilarious.

30:54.486 --> 30:56.353
I stand by that prank.

30:56.355 --> 30:59.122
Look, number five, sisters
don't always get along,

30:59.124 --> 31:00.724
But that doesn't mean
they're not sisters.

31:00.726 --> 31:02.059
Chanel:
See? Exactly.

31:02.061 --> 31:04.061
Thank you, number three.

31:04.063 --> 31:06.063
Okay, now that we're
a sisterhood again,

31:06.065 --> 31:08.799
We have to figure out a way
to get rid of chanel #6.

31:08.801 --> 31:10.300
When you say
get rid of her,

31:10.302 --> 31:11.702
Do you mean, like,
force her to leave,

31:11.704 --> 31:13.170
Or kill her?

31:13.172 --> 31:16.206
Honestly, number five,
do you think I'm insane?

31:16.208 --> 31:18.075
The bitch seduced my boyfriend
into getting her pregnant.

31:18.077 --> 31:20.010
Of course I mean kill her.

31:20.012 --> 31:22.212
Chanel, you cannot just run
around murdering people.

31:22.214 --> 31:24.147
Okay? That just means
you're the killer.

31:24.149 --> 31:26.016
It makes her<i> a</i> killer,
not<i> the</i> killer.

31:26.018 --> 31:27.517
What?

31:27.519 --> 31:29.686
Okay, I just-I just
don't understand

31:29.688 --> 31:31.922
What killing number six
is going to solve.

31:31.924 --> 31:34.358
Um, hello! Everything?

31:34.360 --> 31:37.094
Number six will be dead,
I'll get back my invite

31:37.096 --> 31:39.730
To thanksgiving at the radwell
family compound in the hamptons,

31:39.732 --> 31:41.865
And I'll be back on track
to getting the only thing

31:41.867 --> 31:43.600
A sorority's ever been
good for--

31:43.602 --> 31:45.669
Scoring a hot husband with
an enormous family fortune.

31:45.671 --> 31:47.371
Wait, you just said
that you don't care

31:47.373 --> 31:49.039
About any of those things
and the only thing

31:49.041 --> 31:50.741
That really mattered
to you was sisterhood.

31:50.743 --> 31:52.509
Yeah. That was when
I thought I had taken

31:52.511 --> 31:54.778
Our lifelong friendship for
granted and had lost it forever.

31:54.780 --> 31:57.180
But now that I see
we're stronger than ever,

31:57.182 --> 31:59.016
I.E. Planning
a murder together,

31:59.018 --> 32:01.218
I can concentrate on the things
I care way, way, way more about

32:01.220 --> 32:03.754
Than sisterhood, e.G.
Hot husband, extreme wealth,

32:03.756 --> 32:05.522
Et cetera, et cetera.
Try to keep up.

32:05.524 --> 32:07.090
The logic's not
that complicated.

32:07.092 --> 32:08.425
Now, come on-- murder,

32:08.427 --> 32:09.826
Ideas, go.

32:11.764 --> 32:13.397
I understand
that you're very upset,

32:13.399 --> 32:15.933
But this is a critical time
in our investigation.

32:15.935 --> 32:18.869
Now, deidre is the best
sketch artist in the business.

32:18.871 --> 32:20.904
So, if you can just
close your eyes

32:20.906 --> 32:22.806
And do your best
to describe boone,

32:22.808 --> 32:25.709
We can get a drawing of
the suspect out on the news.

32:25.711 --> 32:28.478
You already have, like,
50 photos of him!

32:28.480 --> 32:29.546
Oh, dear god.

32:29.548 --> 32:31.915
Boone faked his own death.

32:31.917 --> 32:35.819
He has been walking around
campus in a disguise for weeks.

32:35.821 --> 32:38.388
He's murdered 13 people.

32:38.390 --> 32:41.391
We need to call, like,
the fbi or something because

32:41.393 --> 32:44.094
This is clearly out of your
capacity as a detective.

32:44.096 --> 32:46.096
I happen to agree with you.

32:46.098 --> 32:48.065
Which is why I've asked
paul cameron

32:48.067 --> 32:49.833
To come assist
with this investigation.

32:49.835 --> 32:51.601
I'm the founder
of an organization

32:51.603 --> 32:54.838
Called the department of
paranormal exploration or dope.

32:54.840 --> 32:56.606
Chisolm:
I feel it may be time
to let you ladies in

32:56.608 --> 32:57.741
On a little secret.

32:58.911 --> 33:00.610
Since these killings began,

33:00.612 --> 33:03.113
I have focused my investigation
on a single theory--

33:03.115 --> 33:05.916
That the perpetrator
of these murders

33:05.918 --> 33:07.751
Was not being caught...

33:07.753 --> 33:09.753
Because he's a ghost.

33:09.755 --> 33:11.588
Oh, my god.
Now, these
recent developments

33:11.590 --> 33:13.623
Have proven,
much to my horror,

33:13.625 --> 33:15.592
That I am right.
If I may,

33:15.594 --> 33:17.928
I'd like to set up
some of my equipment

33:17.930 --> 33:20.430
To get some
electromagnetic field readings.

33:20.432 --> 33:23.600
Maybe see if the microphones
pick up any ghost chatter.

33:23.602 --> 33:24.768
Now, I must warn you,

33:24.770 --> 33:26.103
If your boyfriend

33:26.105 --> 33:28.338
Was murdered,
he may not be ready

33:28.340 --> 33:30.774
To pass over, and may
come pay you a visitation.

33:30.776 --> 33:32.976
If that happens,

33:32.978 --> 33:36.146
I beg of you,
do not have sex with him.

33:36.148 --> 33:40.317
What is wrong with you?
He's the best in the business.

33:40.319 --> 33:43.653
He had a callback for that
show on the syfy channel

33:43.655 --> 33:46.223
Where they run around
with the night vision goggles.
Look,

33:46.225 --> 33:47.791
Let me handle this.

33:47.793 --> 33:49.393
Oh, like you've handled
all this so far?

33:49.395 --> 33:52.295
All you've done is
sit back and watch

33:52.297 --> 33:54.798
As we've gotten
picked off one by one.

33:54.800 --> 33:58.802
Earl grey was a good man, with
powerful arms and a sexy accent,

33:58.804 --> 34:00.637
And now he's dead.

34:00.639 --> 34:03.774
His blood is on
your hands!

34:08.414 --> 34:10.414
I'm sorry, dean. She's wrong.

34:10.416 --> 34:11.681
No.

34:11.683 --> 34:13.183
She's not.

34:13.185 --> 34:14.584
You know,

34:14.586 --> 34:16.586
The only benefit of meeting you

34:16.588 --> 34:19.423
Is that I now know
I clearly have a type,

34:19.425 --> 34:21.358
And that type is a moron.

34:21.360 --> 34:23.560
I am not only
gonna make sure

34:23.562 --> 34:25.829
That you are taken off
this case and fired,

34:25.831 --> 34:29.566
But I'm gonna make sure
that everyone you know knows

34:29.568 --> 34:33.737
That when we had sex,
you asked me in<i> baby talk</i>

34:33.739 --> 34:35.839
If you could nurse from me.

34:37.076 --> 34:39.142
Please show yourself out.

34:47.553 --> 34:50.787
If you came here to apologize,
we're not interested.

34:50.789 --> 34:51.955
Oh, I never say I'm sorry.

34:51.957 --> 34:53.523
I've done what
I had to do

34:53.525 --> 34:54.724
For the sake
of this school

34:54.726 --> 34:56.259
And my career, both of which

34:56.261 --> 34:57.794
Will be here long after you

34:57.796 --> 35:00.297
Or any of the students here
are gone,

35:00.299 --> 35:02.432
Either through
graduation or death.

35:02.434 --> 35:04.935
I am shocked
that your husband left you.

35:04.937 --> 35:07.270
I do have something

35:07.272 --> 35:08.905
That might be of
interest to you

35:08.907 --> 35:11.341
About that night
in the tub.

35:13.745 --> 35:15.212
There were<i> two</i> babies.

35:15.214 --> 35:17.247
A boy and a girl.

35:17.249 --> 35:19.716
Twins.

35:19.718 --> 35:21.585
After I sent your mother

35:21.587 --> 35:24.454
And her two
slightly less bitchy friends out

35:24.456 --> 35:26.590
To get pillow cases and shovels,

35:26.592 --> 35:30.393
The girl in the tub
let out a death rattle

35:30.395 --> 35:33.930
That was so loud and powerful

35:33.932 --> 35:36.566
That she expelled a second child

35:36.568 --> 35:38.802
From her freshly dead womb.

35:38.804 --> 35:40.437
I knew it!

35:40.439 --> 35:41.771
Congratulations...

35:41.773 --> 35:43.573
On making this moment
all about you.

35:43.575 --> 35:46.276
Are you saying that boone
is the boy baby?

35:46.278 --> 35:47.777
My money's on yes.

35:47.779 --> 35:49.913
That newborn had that same...

35:49.915 --> 35:52.282
Cocky smirk that boone has.

35:52.284 --> 35:55.585
The one girl in the
bathroom who seemed
to have any humanity

35:55.587 --> 35:57.187
Took the babies.

35:57.189 --> 35:59.589
That was the last
I ever saw of them.

35:59.591 --> 36:02.092
But how did the babies end up
in a mental institution?

36:02.094 --> 36:05.529
More importantly, how did
the babies end up with gigi?

36:12.004 --> 36:13.770
I mean, I was wearing
the "sure thing oxford,"

36:13.772 --> 36:15.872
I used the cash chad gave me
to get this awesome hotel suite,

36:15.874 --> 36:18.108
And I basically told her that
my soul could not be at rest

36:18.110 --> 36:20.443
Unless she got naked with me.
Seriously, what kind of person

36:20.445 --> 36:23.380
Just turns their back
on someone's soul like that?

36:23.382 --> 36:25.315
You know,
I'm beginning to think

36:25.317 --> 36:27.851
She's not as amazing
as I thought she was.

36:27.853 --> 36:29.553
No.

36:29.555 --> 36:32.522
Where is gigi? Didn't
you tell her midnight?

36:32.524 --> 36:35.025
Hey, did I show you the knife
I got at the army supply store

36:35.027 --> 36:36.459
To kill her with?

36:36.461 --> 36:38.328
It's super fly.
You're gonna love this.

36:38.330 --> 36:40.497
(exhales)

36:40.499 --> 36:41.865
Ouch. (chuckles)

36:41.867 --> 36:42.866
(lock beeps, clicks)

36:42.868 --> 36:43.934
(door opens)

36:48.507 --> 36:52.175
Oh. I see that you're
enjoying the good life.
Don't start

36:52.177 --> 36:53.476
With the judgment,
gigi, all right?

36:53.478 --> 36:55.045
I've had a really tough day.

36:55.047 --> 36:57.747
You know, there's
an all-points bulletin out

36:57.749 --> 36:59.149
For your arrest.

37:00.352 --> 37:01.851
You jeopardized a plan

37:01.853 --> 37:04.221
That was almost 20 years
in the making

37:04.223 --> 37:06.523
When you kidnapped
zayday. Then...

37:06.525 --> 37:08.892
You disobeyed
my instructions

37:08.894 --> 37:11.861
To only come out
in the devil costume,

37:11.863 --> 37:15.232
And strolled around campus
in broad daylight

37:15.234 --> 37:18.235
Disguised as... Joaquin phoenix.

37:18.237 --> 37:20.570
That disguise was brilliant,
which is more than I can say

37:20.572 --> 37:22.872
For you,
justice scalia.
I'm not finished.

37:22.874 --> 37:24.741
You then...

37:24.743 --> 37:27.177
Have the brilliant idea
of actually going

37:27.179 --> 37:29.412
To kappa as yourself,

37:29.414 --> 37:31.581
Wearing a date shirt
and trying to convince zayday

37:31.583 --> 37:34.684
To sleep with you...
Because you're a ghost.

37:34.686 --> 37:37.420
Boone...

37:37.422 --> 37:38.588
You are...

37:38.590 --> 37:41.324
The weakest link.

37:42.894 --> 37:45.362
I spent the first few months
of my life motherless,

37:45.364 --> 37:48.598
Living off scraps of garbage
and stolen milk.

37:48.600 --> 37:50.767
I grew up in an institution
surrounded by people

37:50.769 --> 37:51.935
That called themselves
timothy busfield

37:51.937 --> 37:53.236
And ate their own poop.

37:53.238 --> 37:54.904
We've followed
all your rules,

37:54.906 --> 37:56.906
Gone along with all your plans,

37:56.908 --> 37:58.141
But I'm the one

37:58.143 --> 37:59.743
Who spent four years of my life

37:59.745 --> 38:02.078
Learning how to slow
my breathing and heart rate down

38:02.080 --> 38:03.813
To the point where
even a trained coroner

38:03.815 --> 38:05.749
Would declare me dead.

38:05.751 --> 38:06.983
I studied film makeup

38:06.985 --> 38:08.618
For eight months straight,

38:08.620 --> 38:10.754
And practiced on the patients,
so I could create

38:10.756 --> 38:12.322
The perfect slash mark
on my throat.

38:12.324 --> 38:14.758
Boone:
I pretended to be gay,

38:14.760 --> 38:16.760
And went undercover
in the dickie dollars scholars,

38:16.762 --> 38:18.628
And I was the one
who masterfully pretended

38:18.630 --> 38:21.965
To attack you with a chain saw
just to get the scent off you.

38:21.967 --> 38:23.767
Are you about
to break into song?

38:23.769 --> 38:26.002
Because all I'm hearing
out of your mouth is,

38:26.004 --> 38:27.437
♪ me, me, me, me, me. ♪

38:27.439 --> 38:29.439
So yes, gigi,
for once in my life,

38:29.441 --> 38:32.008
I went rogue and took
a little something for myself.

38:33.278 --> 38:35.278
My mother would have understood.

38:35.280 --> 38:37.947
But, of course, you don't.

38:37.949 --> 38:40.317
Because no matter
what you like to pretend,

38:40.319 --> 38:41.918
You're not her.

38:41.920 --> 38:43.753
(whispers):
What are you doing?

38:43.755 --> 38:45.422
I'm sorry, gigi.

38:45.424 --> 38:47.657
We're done taking
orders from you.

38:47.659 --> 38:50.093
We're grown-ups now.

38:50.095 --> 38:51.294
It's time for you to go.

38:51.296 --> 38:53.797
What? No. No.

38:53.799 --> 38:55.832
No, no, no!
No! (gasps)

38:58.470 --> 39:00.403
(choking)

39:07.012 --> 39:08.912
(panting)

39:10.682 --> 39:13.016
(exhales)

39:13.018 --> 39:15.618
Your commitment to revenge is...

39:15.620 --> 39:18.388
Clearly greater
than your brother's was.

39:19.691 --> 39:21.725
Should we get some room service?

39:25.997 --> 39:27.997
Hester:
<i>I have to say, chanel,</i>

39:27.999 --> 39:29.799
I am delighted and shocked
that you're letting me keep

39:29.801 --> 39:32.135
Whatever clothes I want--
it's really big of you,

39:32.137 --> 39:35.038
Considering the whole
"I'm pregnant with your
boyfriend's baby" thing.

39:35.040 --> 39:37.040
Well, honestly,
the more I thought about it,

39:37.042 --> 39:38.174
I just realized that

39:38.176 --> 39:39.743
I love chad so much,
and part

39:39.745 --> 39:41.911
Of loving someone is loving
every choice they make,

39:41.913 --> 39:44.981
Regardless of how selfish
and destructive it is, you know?

39:44.983 --> 39:46.750
Thank you, mommy.
Oh, and if you want

39:46.752 --> 39:48.985
To start calling me mommy,
now being that I'm the one

39:48.987 --> 39:50.387
That's gonna
actually be the mommy,

39:50.389 --> 39:52.088
I'm totally fine with that.

39:52.090 --> 39:54.724
Number six, before you
try on that kimono,

39:54.726 --> 39:57.060
Why haven't you had
any of this sushi?

39:57.062 --> 39:59.195
I mean, we got it
just for you.

39:59.197 --> 40:00.930
Mm, don't mind if I do.

40:00.932 --> 40:01.998
(chuckles)

40:03.368 --> 40:05.435
Mmm. That's so good.

40:05.437 --> 40:06.436
Mm-hmm.

40:06.438 --> 40:08.938
Oh, and do yourself a favor,

40:08.940 --> 40:10.039
Have a little slice of that

40:10.041 --> 40:11.908
Soft, unpasteurized cheese.

40:11.910 --> 40:13.743
It makes any sushi

40:13.745 --> 40:15.011
That much more delicious.

40:15.013 --> 40:17.714
Mmm! You're right.

40:17.716 --> 40:21.284
Oh, and, hester, you have<i> got</i>
to taste this champagne.

40:21.286 --> 40:24.354
It's a special champagne
with triple the alcohol and a...

40:24.356 --> 40:27.791
Nicotine-y mouth feel, because
it's infused with tobacco.

40:29.761 --> 40:30.860
Mmm.

40:30.862 --> 40:32.695
De-lish!

40:32.697 --> 40:33.930
Chanel:
Liar!

40:33.932 --> 40:36.032
Hester:
What the hell is going on?

40:36.034 --> 40:38.067
You're trapped
in a web of lies, whore.

40:38.069 --> 40:40.637
You just had sushi,
soft cheese and alcohol--

40:40.639 --> 40:42.906
Three foods that are
damaging to embryos.

40:42.908 --> 40:45.708
Which means you're not pregnant!
That's not true!

40:45.710 --> 40:47.544
I didn't know anything
about the whole...

40:47.546 --> 40:49.479
Sushi-cheese-alcohol thing!

40:49.481 --> 40:50.814
Fine! Prove it.

40:50.816 --> 40:52.081
You're not leaving
this room

40:52.083 --> 40:54.751
Until you've peed
on every single one

40:54.753 --> 40:56.319
Of these pregnancy tests.

40:57.956 --> 40:59.889
(chuckles)

40:59.891 --> 41:04.127
Hmm... I had all three
of you fooled, didn't I!

41:04.129 --> 41:06.396
Fine, you got me.
I'm not pregnant.

41:06.398 --> 41:09.132
But it doesn't matter, because
chad still thinks that I am,

41:09.134 --> 41:11.734
And being that he already
purchased our first-class
airfare to the hamptons,

41:11.736 --> 41:14.604
That means that I'll be the
one attending thanksgiving,
where I'll have

41:14.606 --> 41:17.941
Ample opportunity to get
pregnant all weekend long!

41:17.943 --> 41:19.809
(gasps quietly)

41:19.811 --> 41:24.080
Chanel (screeching):
I'll kill you, neckbrace...!

41:24.082 --> 41:25.682
(shrieking)

41:32.424 --> 41:34.357
Hester, I'm sorry.

41:36.461 --> 41:38.595
What did you say?

41:38.597 --> 41:41.097
Hester, I am so sorry.

41:41.099 --> 41:43.266
I'm sorry you've had
to go through life

41:43.268 --> 41:45.268
Feeling like an outcast, and...

41:45.270 --> 41:46.936
I'm sorry that I got angry

41:46.938 --> 41:49.772
That chad's
clearly chosen you over me.

41:49.774 --> 41:52.375
It's just that
ever since

41:52.377 --> 41:54.377
You walked
through those doors...

41:54.379 --> 41:58.147
I knew you were gonna be the one
to take it all away from me.

41:58.149 --> 41:59.282
Really?

41:59.284 --> 42:01.451
No.

42:03.788 --> 42:06.389
(scream echoing)

42:18.169 --> 42:19.869
(chanel gasps)
(bone cracks)

42:22.507 --> 42:24.207
(crying):
Oh, my god.

42:27.012 --> 42:27.911
You killed her!

42:27.913 --> 42:30.313
Chanel #6 is dead!

42:30.315 --> 42:31.748
I realize that
my killing neckbrace

42:31.750 --> 42:33.683
Might just seem
like a bridge too far,

42:33.685 --> 42:35.852
But trust me when I say
this had to happen.

42:35.854 --> 42:37.420
And I'm confident
that I'll be able

42:37.422 --> 42:40.256
To redeem myself morally
in everyone's eyes.

42:40.258 --> 42:42.725
(sighs)
and furthermore,

42:42.727 --> 42:45.929
What I just did will become
a<i> new</i> ghost story.

42:45.931 --> 42:48.164
A cautionary tale

42:48.166 --> 42:50.500
About what happens
to hog-faced bitches

42:50.502 --> 42:53.169
Who try to steal
hotter kappas' boyfriends.

42:53.171 --> 42:56.005
A story that'll be told
around the campfire

42:56.007 --> 42:59.909
By kappa pledges
for centuries to come.

42:59.911 --> 43:01.744
(chanel chuckles)

43:01.746 --> 43:03.246
(takes deep breath)

43:03.248 --> 43:06.416
Okay... Let's get her
in that meat locker.

